    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "What is the weight limit for a gravity roller conveyor?",
      "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Standard light-duty gravity roller conveyors handle up to 50-75 lbs per product. Medium-duty gravity rollers handle 75-200 lbs. Heavy-duty gravity roller sections with 2.5 to 3.5 inch diameter rollers and structural frames can handle up to 500+ lbs. The capacity depends on roller diameter, wall thickness, bearing grade, axle size, and frame gauge." }
